contentrichtext.text: {{For|a German alcoholic beverage family company|BEHN}} '''{{PAGENAME}}''' is a surname. Notable persons with that surname include: * [[Aphra Behn]] (c. 1640–1689), English prolific dramatist * [[Ari Behn]] (born 1972), Norwegian author, husband of Princess Märtha Louise of Norway * [[Hernan Behn]], Puerto Rican businessman, brother of Sosthenes Behn * [[Harry Behn]] (1898–1973), also known as Giles Behn, American screenwriter and children's author * [[Jerry Behn]] (born 1954), American politician * [[Noel Behn]] (1928? - 1998) was an American novelist ([[The Kremlin Letter]]), screenwriter and theatrical producer * [[Sosthenes Behn]] (1882–1957), Puerto Rican businessman, brother of Hernan Behn ==See also== * [[Benn]] {{Surname}}
